						<summary>

						<p>Uttarāpatīśvara temple, main <hi rend="italic">gōpuram,</hi> right of entrance.</p>						

						<p><hi rend="bold">••• •••• Prajāpati, Vaikāśi 20.</hi></p>						

						<p>Damaged and in corrupt language. It is in late characters. It refers to some chief and his agent (both names are damaged) and to the rate of levy in gold probably on different kinds of looms.</p>						

